description: Fantastic opportunity to own this amazing single family home in a great location complete with TWO off street parking spots!!! This updated home has an oversized master suite complete with sitting room and full bathroom.  The kitchen is bright and open with a pantry and charming tin ceiling.  Out back there is a deck overlooking an adorable yard.  Enjoy the lifestyle of living just blocks from the gorgeous South Boston Beaches and the West Broadway and East Broadway Shops.  Just around the way from the Dorchester Heights George Washington Monument as well as the improved L Street Bathhouse.  Call today for a showing.
